250 Recipient='nobody@example.com'.^M
354 End your message with a period on a line by itself.^M
554 This message contains prohibited content^M

<result "last word">
250 Sender=''.^M
250 Recipient='nobody@example.com'.^M
354 End your message with a period on a line by itself.^M
554 This message contains prohibited content^M

<result "middle word middle">
250 Sender=''.^M
250 Recipient='nobody@example.com'.^M
354 End your message with a period on a line by itself.^M
554 This message contains prohibited content^M

<result "word">
250 Sender=''.^M
